text: Malomusino () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilkineyevsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 97 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Yermolayevo, 5 km from Ilkineyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Malomusino
